{"tid":453494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平上海視察 高鐵沿線300公尺所有企業於放半天假","createTime":"2017-10-31T08:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T09:59:31.000Z","uid":47352,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7181fd9a24673675ea940645e196b2deb14b84d8","tid":453494,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:28:02.000Z","msg":"習近平31日下午將到中國上海視察，傳出上海警方要求高鐵沿線300公尺內兩側企業人車全部淨空，強調「如不配合，後果自負」。<br />\n據美國自由亞洲電台（RFA）報導，上海公安局發出緊急通知，要求「高鐵沿線300公尺兩側所有企業於今日(31日)12點起全部放半天假，辦公場所內不得有人辦公，所有場地地面不准停放車輛，所有客戶地面車輛全部駛離」並且強調如不配合，後果自負。<br />\n許多在高鐵沿線上班的網友，紛紛在《推特》上貼出這份「緊急通知」，並酸「據說全世界第一男子天團馬上蒞臨上海」、「迴避，肅靜，皇帝出巡了」、「大大來上海，你們讓開」、「人民是他的大敵」、「5年前還鼓吹不封路」。（即時新聞中心／"},{"pid":"ab908d7bea04c5e0689d324e2f769a443012d331","tid":453494,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:29:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c961df18b589d8010ad584fc0d8c8ee80e6ecc7e","tid":453494,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:31:20.000Z","msg":"古代皇帝出巡都係差唔多 好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96adec0dfe8d062bd90b8094c8c79f856b3d03e5","tid":453494,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:33:03.000Z","msg":"幾時黎香港睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91498350f0ba4227897694ddc555edf1261d63aa","tid":453494,"uid":28151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時黎香港睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n挑, 7.1 嗰排都冇得放啦"},{"pid":"f6bab499c80c9a7fe11192521c6c9df1ea997861","tid":453494,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾時黎香港睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n挑, 7.1 嗰排都冇得放啦</blockquote><br />\nICC唔比